1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Effective leaders balance credibility with humility and a willingness to learn.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:08,000
However, not every question will help you get ahead.

3
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:12,880
You need to know how, when, and why you're asking to be more influential.

4
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:19,600
Good questions are concise, build on what others have said, and revolve around a focused idea.

5
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:21,920
Consider your intention before asking.

6
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:26,320
Are you trying to show understanding, interest, or help someone see another perspective?


